/ : ; \< = \> ? @ \[ \\ \] \` { \| }
7. Times and timestamps present in resources returned by API calls will be in UTC (see Date and Time Formats).
8. "Data Field Names" should not be provided if the value is empty.
9. Alphanumeric special fields accept all UTF-8 characters except { } \| \~ \\
10. Unicode fields accept all unicode characters except { } \| \~ \\

